{
  "number": 78,
  "name": "سُورَةُ النَّبَإِ",
  "englishName": "An-Naba",
  "englishNameTranslation": "The Announcement",
  "revelationType": "Meccan",
  "ayahs": [
    {
      "number": 5673,
      "text": "ABOUT WHAT do they [most often] ask one another?",
      "numberInSurah": 1,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 582,
      "ruku": 518,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5674,
      "text": "About the awesome tiding [of resurrection],",
      "numberInSurah": 2,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 582,
      "ruku": 518,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5675,
      "text": "on which they [so utterly] disagree.",
      "numberInSurah": 3,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 582,
      "ruku": 518,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5676,
      "text": "Nay, but in time they will come to understand [it]!",
      "numberInSurah": 4,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 582,
      "ruku": 518,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5677,
      "text": "And once again: Nay, but in time they will come to understand!",
      "numberInSurah": 5,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 582,
      "ruku": 518,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5678,
      "text": "HAVE WE NOT made the earth a resting-place [for you],",
      "numberInSurah": 6,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 582,
      "ruku": 518,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5679,
      "text": "and the mountains [its] pegs?",
      "numberInSurah": 7,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 582,
      "ruku": 518,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5680,
      "text": "And We have created you in pairs;",
      "numberInSurah": 8,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 582,
      "ruku": 518,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5681,
      "text": "and We have made your sleep [a symbol of] death",
      "numberInSurah": 9,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 582,
      "ruku": 518,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5682,
      "text": "and made the night [its] cloak",
      "numberInSurah": 10,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 582,
      "ruku": 518,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5683,
      "text": "and made the day [a symbol of] life.",
      "numberInSurah": 11,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 582,
      "ruku": 518,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5684,
      "text": "And We have built above you seven firmaments,",
      "numberInSurah": 12,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 582,
      "ruku": 518,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5685,
      "text": "and have placed [therein the sun,] a lamp full of blazing splendour.",
      "numberInSurah": 13,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 582,
      "ruku": 518,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5686,
      "text": "And from the wind-driven clouds We send down waters pouring in abundance,",
      "numberInSurah": 14,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 582,
      "ruku": 518,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5687,
      "text": "so that We might bring forth thereby grain, and herbs,",
      "numberInSurah": 15,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 582,
      "ruku": 518,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5688,
      "text": "and gardens dense with follage.",
      "numberInSurah": 16,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 582,
      "ruku": 518,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5689,
      "text": "VERILY, the Day of Distinction [between the true and the false] has indeed its appointed time:",
      "numberInSurah": 17,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 582,
      "ruku": 518,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5690,
      "text": "the Day when the trumpet [of resurrection] is sounded and you all come forward in multitudes;",
      "numberInSurah": 18,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 582,
      "ruku": 518,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5691,
      "text": "and when the skies are opened and become [as wide-flung] gates;",
      "numberInSurah": 19,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 582,
      "ruku": 518,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5692,
      "text": "and when the mountains are made to vanish as if they had been a mirage.",
      "numberInSurah": 20,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 582,
      "ruku": 518,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5693,
      "text": "[On that Day,] verily, hell will lie in wait [for those who deny the truth] –",
      "numberInSurah": 21,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 582,
      "ruku": 518,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5694,
      "text": "a goal for all who are wont to transgress the bounds of what is right!",
      "numberInSurah": 22,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 582,
      "ruku": 518,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5695,
      "text": "In it shall they remain for a long time.",
      "numberInSurah": 23,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 582,
      "ruku": 518,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5696,
      "text": "Neither coolness shall they taste therein nor any [thirst-quenching] drink –",
      "numberInSurah": 24,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 582,
      "ruku": 518,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5697,
      "text": "only burning despair and ice-cold darkness:",
      "numberInSurah": 25,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 582,
      "ruku": 518,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5698,
      "text": "a meet requital [for their sins]!",
      "numberInSurah": 26,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 582,
      "ruku": 518,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5699,
      "text": "Behold, they were not expecting to be called to account,",
      "numberInSurah": 27,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 582,
      "ruku": 518,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5700,
      "text": "having given the lie to Our messages one and all:",
      "numberInSurah": 28,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 582,
      "ruku": 518,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5701,
      "text": "but We have placed on record every single thing [of what they did].",
      "numberInSurah": 29,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 582,
      "ruku": 518,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5702,
      "text": "[And so We shall say:] \"Taste, then, [the fruit of your evil doings,] for now We shall bestow on you nothing but more and more suffering!\"",
      "numberInSurah": 30,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 582,
      "ruku": 518,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5703,
      "text": "[But,] verily for the God-conscious there is supreme fulfilment in store:",
      "numberInSurah": 31,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 583,
      "ruku": 519,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5704,
      "text": "luxuriant gardens and vinyards,",
      "numberInSurah": 32,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 583,
      "ruku": 519,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5705,
      "text": "and splendid companions well matched,",
      "numberInSurah": 33,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 583,
      "ruku": 519,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5706,
      "text": "and a cup [of happiness] overflowing.",
      "numberInSurah": 34,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 583,
      "ruku": 519,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5707,
      "text": "No empty talk will they hear in that [paradise], nor any lie.",
      "numberInSurah": 35,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 583,
      "ruku": 519,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5708,
      "text": "[All this will be] a reward from thy Sustainer, a gift in accordance with [His Own] reckoning –",
      "numberInSurah": 36,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 583,
      "ruku": 519,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5709,
      "text": "[a reward from] the Sustainer of the heavens and the earth and all that is between them, the Most Gracious! [And] none shall have it in their power to raise their voices unto Him",
      "numberInSurah": 37,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 583,
      "ruku": 519,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5710,
      "text": "on the Day when all [human] souls and all the angels will stand up in ranks: none will speak but he to whom the Most Gracious will have given leave; and [everyone] will say [only] what is right.",
      "numberInSurah": 38,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 583,
      "ruku": 519,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5711,
      "text": "That will be the Day of Ultimate Truth: whoever wills, then, let him take the path that leads towards his Sustainer!",
      "numberInSurah": 39,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 583,
      "ruku": 519,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5712,
      "text": "Verily, We have warned you of suffering near at hand - [suffering] on the Day when man shall [clearly] see what his hands have sent ahead, and when he who has denied the truth shall say, \"Oh, would that I were mere dust...!\"",
      "numberInSurah": 40,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 583,
      "ruku": 519,
      "hizbQuarter": 233,
      "sajda": false
    }
  ],
